{"tid":1867870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"醫護罷工失敗，其他行業罷工都唔會成功","createTime":"2020-02-07T10:34:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T11:34:39.000Z","uid":104767,"like":5,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"de638763e6c1da3c29bddb62273f0c082aaa207d","tid":1867870,"uid":104767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:34:00.000Z","msg":"罷工可否威脅政府，取決於係咪可以影響政府春袋，即係可唔可以阻止政府為中國權貴服務。<br />\n香港對中國權貴有用嘅地方向來只有<br />\n1. 港交所<br />\n2. 港幣<br />\n3. 機場<br />\n所以只有金融界同機場界全面罷工先可以威脅政府，但係前者已被中國人侵佔，後者有領空依個春袋，所以唔會罷得成工。<br />\n另外香港局勢保持可控先可以為權貴服務，所以警察罷工有效，但係講出嚟自己都笑<br />\n<br />\n由於有新沙士，香港可以為中共服務嘅地方多咗兩個<br />\n4. 醫療系統<br />\n5. 出境渠道<br />\n<br />\n所以只有醫護罷工先可以真正威脅政府，但係要有縱使無法救治港人，亦不要為中國人送死嘅決心。其他行業除咗關口公務員都做唔到依個效果。<br />\n<br />\n如果香港抗共失敗，醫護復工必被寫成滑鐵盧戰役載入史冊。"},{"pid":"0416ce3a0df92f90a62a682745039a62dd23f9ed","tid":1867870,"uid":317233,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:34:58.000Z","msg":"自己唔罷憑咩要醫護為你罷<br />\n<br />\n有冇醫生/藥劑師/科學家可以解答吓<br />\n除咗Remdesivir，點解唔用PMO去醫治/預防WARS<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1867613\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1867613</a>"},{"pid":"8cd7936ed8e82ee25488c16a56a07ee764559914","tid":1867870,"uid":104767,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:35:37.000Z","msg":"以為大三罷可以左右政府決定根本太天真"},{"pid":"19fb94db7aa0db615abc845c69a613dd2d789473","tid":1867870,"uid":104767,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0416ce3a0df92f90a62a682745039a62dd23f9ed","tid":1867870,"uid":317233,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:34:58.000Z","msg":"自己唔罷憑咩要醫護為你罷<br />\n<br />\n有冇醫生/藥劑師/科學家可以解答吓<br />\n除咗Remdesivir，點解唔用PMO去醫治/預防WARS<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1867613\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1867613</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:36:39.000Z","msg":"你智商幾多？講明只有醫護罷工有效"},{"pid":"4b60620872d84b13a3ecf4d737e52e64b72287eb","tid":1867870,"uid":17163,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:37:11.000Z","msg":"講個笑話你聽 : 香港人搞革命"},{"pid":"69d7f6116415b27dd7bd9faf8909132f13e16cc5","tid":1867870,"uid":23481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:37:54.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"7965ac48b848d77feee43dc17b71765c3af0cdbd","tid":1867870,"uid":317233,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"19fb94db7aa0db615abc845c69a613dd2d789473","tid":1867870,"uid":104767,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0416ce3a0df92f90a62a682745039a62dd23f9ed","tid":1867870,"uid":317233,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:34:58.000Z","msg":"自己唔罷憑咩要醫護為你罷<br />\n<br />\n有冇醫生/藥劑師/科學家可以解答吓<br />\n除咗Remdesivir，點解唔用PMO去醫治/預防WARS<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1867613\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1867613</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:36:39.000Z","msg":"你智商幾多？講明只有醫護罷工有效"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:40:00.000Z","msg":"who are you？你係大台?"},{"pid":"13088da9db5daf58917b6c97513a7470ce0cd5df","tid":1867870,"uid":107577,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:41:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>即使醫護唔繼續罷<br />\n佢地都係成功！<br />\n<br />\n唔罷 唔等於 失敗<br />\n如果一陣投票結果係唔繼續<br />\n都唔可以 spin 到係失敗<br />\n記住,大家要既係士氣<br />\n連 HA 工會都自認失敗，咁就咬住食。<br />\n重申,唔繼續罷 不等於 失敗<br />\n<br />\n係政府同 HA 不聽訴求 專制橫蠻<br />\n<br />\n記者會同會員大會做個小總結<br />\n講大家成功做咗 d 咩<br />\n增加士氣<br />\n唔好淨係 FOCUS 政府冇做 d 咩先。<br />\neg<br />\n- 有幾多人參加咗工會<br />\n- 呢幾日有幾多人罷工<br />\n- 令到政府由唔封關，到局部封關（但仍唔足夠），都係醫護罷工所 做到既其中一個成果<br />\n- 令大家長遠關注同監察 HA 資源問題，對 HA, 醫護，病人都係好事<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gLrYQB4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgLrYQB4.jpg&h=f72ededb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6SwmOoL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6SwmOoL.png&h=96bc9ec5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b0446de0aea80f30be827b6c948ae43261232a0f","tid":1867870,"uid":104767,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7965ac48b848d77feee43dc17b71765c3af0cdbd","tid":1867870,"uid":317233,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"19fb94db7aa0db615abc845c69a613dd2d789473","tid":1867870,"uid":104767,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0416ce3a0df92f90a62a682745039a62dd23f9ed","tid":1867870,"uid":317233,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:34:58.000Z","msg":"自己唔罷憑咩要醫護為你罷<br />\n<br />\n有冇醫生/藥劑師/科學家可以解答吓<br />\n除咗Remdesivir，點解唔用PMO去醫治/預防WARS<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1867613\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1867613</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:36:39.000Z","msg":"你智商幾多？講明只有醫護罷工有效"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:40:00.000Z","msg":"who are you？你係大台?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:42:49.000Z","msg":"問who are you 冇用的。自己睇下上面段野合唔合理，覺得有邏輯謬誤請指出，咁先可以搵到新方向"},{"pid":"f1597a1b93631e8740c220da4df3136accaeef75","tid":1867870,"uid":201178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:45:04.000Z","msg":"運輸罷工點睇?"},{"pid":"ff9443a734c537e13d1894945b322d9d685c1ff7","tid":1867870,"uid":181747,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:45:18.000Z","msg":"大三罷對港共係冇影響<br />\n稅照收人工照出<br />\n唔係民選既政府係唔會care人民既利益"},{"pid":"425bcc73a83bcf173abeb34cfb97547cc6d3afa8","tid":1867870,"uid":104767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1597a1b93631e8740c220da4df3136accaeef75","tid":1867870,"uid":201178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:45:04.000Z","msg":"運輸罷工點睇?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:47:25.000Z","msg":"只有貨運有效<br />\n客運罷工只會阻港豬返工，影響只係港豬而非政府"},{"pid":"a1ef3a27cc92829c58d3a07289a3fc0938bb2f58","tid":1867870,"uid":148355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:49:57.000Z","msg":"你係咪以為罷得5日就可以成功爭取？香港人太急功近利，醫護罷工令到政府一星期公佈咁多措施已經做得好好"},{"pid":"33b4e17477c904feacfa91625231f9b92674fd72","tid":1867870,"uid":158270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8cd7936ed8e82ee25488c16a56a07ee764559914","tid":1867870,"uid":104767,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:35:37.000Z","msg":"以為大三罷可以左右政府決定根本太天真"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:52:46.000Z","msg":"同意。香港抗爭者以為香港政府係西方民主政府係嚴重誤判，香港政府只不過係中共統戰香港特權階級嘅組織，唔係為民服務。<br />\n佢嘅下場只會係另一個遠東共和國。任何服從或請求，都只會徒增佢嘅認受性。"},{"pid":"b80903e2e6b67ad5473ecc82443d563b68e81c39","tid":1867870,"uid":104767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1ef3a27cc92829c58d3a07289a3fc0938bb2f58","tid":1867870,"uid":148355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:49:57.000Z","msg":"你係咪以為罷得5日就可以成功爭取？香港人太急功近利，醫護罷工令到政府一星期公佈咁多措施已經做得好好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:54:04.000Z","msg":"所以應該繼續而非宣佈階段性勝利然後復工"},{"pid":"a37a82b81df356fae4d0bf2f880fbee272a5f1d2","tid":1867870,"uid":148355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b80903e2e6b67ad5473ecc82443d563b68e81c39","tid":1867870,"uid":104767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1ef3a27cc92829c58d3a07289a3fc0938bb2f58","tid":1867870,"uid":148355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:49:57.000Z","msg":"你係咪以為罷得5日就可以成功爭取？香港人太急功近利，醫護罷工令到政府一星期公佈咁多措施已經做得好好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:54:04.000Z","msg":"所以應該繼續而非宣佈階段性勝利然後復工"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:56:06.000Z","msg":"咁依家佢地做咗決定我地都應該尊重，而唔係放負"},{"pid":"0d97cd18815e51741b28b78fbc8366a717acd77d","tid":1867870,"uid":104767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a37a82b81df356fae4d0bf2f880fbee272a5f1d2","tid":1867870,"uid":148355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b80903e2e6b67ad5473ecc82443d563b68e81c39","tid":1867870,"uid":104767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1ef3a27cc92829c58d3a07289a3fc0938bb2f58","tid":1867870,"uid":148355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:49:57.000Z","msg":"你係咪以為罷得5日就可以成功爭取？香港人太急功近利，醫護罷工令到政府一星期公佈咁多措施已經做得好好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:54:04.000Z","msg":"所以應該繼續而非宣佈階段性勝利然後復工"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:56:06.000Z","msg":"咁依家佢地做咗決定我地都應該尊重，而唔係放負"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:01:21.000Z","msg":"唔係放負，而係復工決定客觀上係錯棋。<br />\n我尊重醫護專業但係會批評佢哋今次決定"},{"pid":"226088693e09df34cb1bf113bd8fab7cdeed483b","tid":1867870,"uid":104767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:22:39.000Z","msg":"只有醫護罷工先可以真正威脅政府，但係要有縱使無法救治港人，亦不要為中國人送死嘅決心。其他行業除咗關口公務員同物流業界都做唔到依個效果。"},{"pid":"87be825ee4cd537271169c39245ec0c7f163f08a","tid":1867870,"uid":300165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:23:15.000Z","msg":"醫護可以再罷工<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1867792/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1867792/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"949e4f29f0746dbc0578b62cecbe1215a71cf8f0","tid":1867870,"uid":104767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87be825ee4cd537271169c39245ec0c7f163f08a","tid":1867870,"uid":300165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:23:15.000Z","msg":"醫護可以再罷工<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1867792/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1867792/page/1</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:26:33.000Z","msg":"好難，未爆已經復工，爆咗更加唔會罷<br />\n香港醫護除咗Hippocratic Oath 外唔會接受其他價值"},{"pid":"ef52f972c7e467e4999088c545e67378ea9960a1","tid":1867870,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:30:41.000Z","msg":"[突發]港龍工會都宣佈要搞罷工啦!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1867988\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1867988</a>"},{"pid":"a112b886fcea752f1ea50582249c2dce83905aab","tid":1867870,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:31:06.000Z","msg":"既然香港暫時勇武同罷工都係唔可行，咁唯有 焦土<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1868045\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1868045</a><br />\n<br />\n[香港人，反抗] 要贏，必須升級至 全民三罷，甚至 全民勇武<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1866282\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1866282</a><br />\n<br />\n無論係 <span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">勇武</span></strong></span> 或者 <strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">罷緊工</span></span></strong> 既手足 都捱唔到好耐<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">「我地以為一二一二係衝，點知人地一二一二係退既。」<br />\n<br />\n「望返後面已經冇晒人。」<br />\n<br />\n「如果佢話三罷，或者罷鐵、罷藍舖頭，講完你要真係做先得架。」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n擺在面前有兩套方法，<br />\n其一是  <span style=\"color: limegreen;\">全民有心理準備作正面衝突</span>，<br />\n其二是  <span style=\"color: limegreen;\">全民落實罷工</span><br />\n<br />\n「但係好多人就係覺得，去到呢個樽頸唔知點做。其實佢心入面明明就知呢兩樣野。」</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「希望大家唔好淨係識得講香港人反抗，反抗係做出?架，唔係你鳩?架！」</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「我地個個都有夢想架，我地個個都有?野想做，但係，我地肯犧牲??野?上前線爭取啊！」</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n勇武 同 醫護 都唔係condom，<br />\n所有珍惜生命既香港人，<br />\n以及願意付出更多既抗爭者，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">請你地加入呢次罷工！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n對於全民勇武已經唔抱太大既希望，但係呢次武漢肺炎係一個發動罷工既大好機會<br />\n希望全香港人可以真正團結一次<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9vzoa9L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9vzoa9L.png&h=f8666165&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3479a0b8149845ef0562f932c4c27e8da2b75c1d","tid":1867870,"uid":104767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a112b886fcea752f1ea50582249c2dce83905aab","tid":1867870,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T11:31:06.000Z","msg":"既然香港暫時勇武同罷工都係唔可行，咁唯有 焦土<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n